{"tid":214021,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"係教會識嘅女朋友係ptgf...","createTime":"2017-04-23T13:32:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-23T17:36:22.000Z","uid":52254,"like":30,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"354fe1495e92f47945152e76deaf52136d93ec8b","tid":214021,"uid":52254,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:32:28.000Z","msg":"事源係早幾日連登爆左個ptgf個post <br />\n小弟抱著花生友嘅心態諗住睇下有無女我係識嘅<br />\n一開頭我都down唔到啲相<br />\n點知有個fd down左就同我開心share<br />\n睇下睇下竟然見到我係教會識嘅女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後我send比佢睇<br />\n佢話佢無做過 係比人借刀<br />\n但係佢住公屋 <br />\n佢屋企人又唔似會有閒錢比佢買iphone<br />\n平時同我出街就成日玩電話<br />\n我就開始覺得佢係講大話<br />\n然後佢同我講話不如出黎傾<br />\n我就話有咩唔可以係whatsapp傾 要出去傾<br />\n佢無應我<br />\n我就同佢講話其實無所謂<br />\n只要無同人扑過我都無問題<br />\n佢無應我<br />\n我再問 咁你接過幾多個客<br />\n佢話6個<br />\n我又問 個個都屌過你？<br />\n佢話係<br />\n我覺得佢好污糟<br />\n佢之前建立嘅乖乖女形象已經無曬<br />\n咁我又問 你搵左幾多？<br />\n佢話萬幾<br />\n我話 你要啲錢黎做咩<br />\n佢話 想同我去旅行<br />\n我喊左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53593b02cae4f717dc18600fff02bb1c53a82c0d","tid":214021,"uid":104260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:35:05.000Z","msg":"你做第7個 而且係最後一個屌佢既咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89fdcceca308e5194dc57424618befa686346570","tid":214021,"uid":95394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:35:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aff41674d5458ba914156be86b9bfa6fd382bd5","tid":214021,"uid":17880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:36:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"604139f3caa62d702155a29f4115bdd7bd6ab387","tid":214021,"uid":36981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:36:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4377cabd68cb2